  "readme_html": "<pre><code>git clone https://github.com/ThomasJanssen-tech/Local-RAG-with-Ollama\ncd Local-RAG-With-Ollama\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code>python -m venv venv\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code>venv\\Scripts\\Activate\n(or on Mac): source venv/bin/activate\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code>pip install -r requirements.txt\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Open a terminal in VS Code</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Execute the following command:</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>python run 1_scraping_wikipedia.py\npython run 2_chunking_embedding_ingestion.py\nstreamlit run 3_chatbot.py\n</code></pre>",
